# 🔐 Authentication & Authorization API

A Node.js REST API built with **Express.js**, **MongoDB**, and **JWT** for secure user authentication and authorization.  
It follows the **MVC pattern**, includes **JWT-based bearer token authentication**, and provides clean API responses.

---

## 🚀 Live Demo

- 🌐 [Render Deployment](https://authendication-authorization-1-qzdr.onrender.com)

---

## 📂 Repository

- 📌 [GitHub Repository](https://github.com/Sajitha94/Authendication---Authorization)

---

## ✨ Features

- ✅ User Registration with **hashed passwords** (bcryptjs)
- ✅ User Login with **JWT token generation**
- ✅ **Bearer Token Authentication** middleware for protected routes
- ✅ Centralized error handling
- ✅ MVC architecture (Models, Controllers, Routes)
- ✅ MongoDB connection using Mongoose
- ✅ Well-structured & extendable codebase

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

- **Backend:** Node.js, Express.js
- **Database:** MongoDB (Mongoose ODM)
- **Authentication:** JWT, bcryptjs
- **Environment Management:** dotenv

---

